1. Welcome to FinSight Bank
FinSight Bank offers a full range of modern, transparent, and secure financial solutions tailored to individuals, professionals, and businesses.
Our commitment: clarity, accessibility, and digital efficiency in every service we provide.

4. Financing and Credit Solutions
Personal Credit: education, health, or personal projects; repayment 3–60 months.
Auto Loan: up to 90% of vehicle value; 12–72 months; approval within 48h.
Housing Loan: purchase or construction; up to 25 years; rate indexed to TMM + margin.
SME Credit: working capital or investment; SOTUGAR guarantee; advisory support.

FinSight Online – secure web portal: account consultation, transfers, bill payments.
FinSight Mobile App: instant balances, QR payments, card management.
